<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8'>
    <title>A Postcard For You!</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-9aIt2nRpC12Uk9gS9baDl411NQApFmC26EwAOH8WgZl5MYYxFfc+NcPb1dKGj7Sk" crossorigin="anonymous">
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Hello From Afar</h1>
    <p>Dear @Model.Recipient,</p>
    <p>How are you? I hope that you are having a nice weekend. I'm vacationing in @Model.Destination while I learn @Model.Activity! </p>
    <p>@Model.Recipient, you would not believe how awesome it is here!</p>
    <p>But I like @Model.Activity a lot, so I've got that going for me. </p>
    <p>Looking forward to seeing you soon. I'll bring you back @Model.Souvenirs .</p>
    <p>Cheers,</p>
    <p>Travel Enthusiast @Model.Sender</p>
  </body>
</html>